<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "IMG_5393.jpeg", width: 260, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated <%= progressbar_colors %>"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%=	 skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>


          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p><b>Everywhere Software</b> is a technology company founded by Dontrell Washington.</p>
        <p> My goal is simplifying the relationship between client and developer. Too often, developers fail to
          communicate with clients throughout the development stages of a project, resulting in a product that fails to
          reach the customer's end goal.</p>
        <p>For this reason, I utilize a development pattern that focuses on constant communication and transparent
          design templates. My projects are crafted to the client's specifications by giving daily updates. This ensures
          a product aligning with the client's objective. The end result is the right product.</p>

        <p>
          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
        <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
          <div class="card card-body">
            Job 1
          </div>
          <div class="card card-body">
            Job 2
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse" id="education">
          <div class="card card-body">
            School 1
          </div>
          <div class="card card-body">
            School 2
          </div>
        </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




